    public class HIButtonOptions
extends java.lang.Object
implements HIChartsJSONSerializable
    description: A collection of options for buttons appearing in the exporting module. In styled mode, the buttons are styled with the .highcharts-contextbutton and .highcharts-button-symbol class.
